argin-bottom:0px;\"><tbody>    <tr class=\"odd\" data-item-user=\"748427\">\r\n    <td class=\"subject\"><a href=\"/subject/topic/30309\" title=\"有哪些“完蛋”系的真人后宫游戏是有h的？\" class=\"l\">有哪些“完蛋”系的真人后宫游戏是有h的？</a></td>\r\n    <td width=\"15%\"><a href=\"/user/748427\">符腾堡公爵</a></td>\r\n    <td width=\"15%\" align=\"right\"><small class=\"grey\">1 replies</small></td>\r\n    <td width=\"15%\" align=\"right\"><small class=\"grey\">2024-6-20</small></td>\r\n    </tr>    <tr class=\"even\" data-item-user=\"823806\">\r\n    <td class=\"subject\"><a href=\"/subject/topic/27597\" title=\"《完蛋》之后，会重走“美少女游戏”的旧路吗\" class=\"l\">《完蛋》之后，会重走“美少女游戏”的旧路吗</a></td>\r\n    <td width=\"15%\"><a href=\"/user/823806\">bust3r</a></td>\r\n    <td width=\"15%\" align=\"right\"><small class=\"grey\">19 replies</small></td>\r\n    <td width=\"15%\" align=\"right\"><small class=\"grey\">2023-11-7</small></td>\r\n    </tr><tr><td>&nbsp</td><td width=\"15%\"></td><td width=\"15%\"></td><td width=\"15%\" align=\"right\"><a href=\"/subject/460529/board\" class=\"more\">更多讨论 »</a></td></tr>\r\n</tbody></table>\r\n\r\n</div><div class=\"subject_section\">\n<h2 class=\"subtitle\">吐槽箱</h2><div id=\"comment_box\" class=\"comment-box comment_box_lr\">\n<div class=\"item clearit\" data-item-user=\"1145899\">\n<a href=\"/user/1145899\" class=\"avatar\"><span class=\"avatarNeue avatarSize32 ll\" style=\"background-image:url('//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/l/001/14/58/1145899_x8l8L.jpg?r=1765284850&hd=1')\"></span></a>\n<div class=\"text_container text_main_even\">\n<div class=\"text\">\n<div class=\"actions_container\">\n<div class=\"post_actions\"></div>\n</div>\n\n    \t\t<a href=\"/user/1145899\" class=\"l\">帅哥的大哥大</a>\n<span class=\"starstop-s\"><span class=\"starlight stars1\"></span></span><small class=\"grey\"> 玩过 </small>\n<small class=\"grey\">@ 2025-11-16 00:49</small>\n    \t\t<p class=\"comment\">跟风玩的，从某种方面来讲它让我重新回坑了galgame，也算是一件好事。</p><div class=\"likes_grid\" id=\"likes_grid_45273359\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"item clearit\" data-item-user=\"368176\">\n<a href=\"/user/368176\" class=\"avatar\"><span class=\"avatarNeue avatarSize32 ll\" style=\"background-image:url('//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/l/000/36/81/368176.jpg?r=1704803712&hd=1')\"></span></a>\n<div class=\"text_container text_main_even\">\n<div class=\"text\">\n<div class=\"actions_container\">\n<div class=\"post_actions\"></div>\n</div>\n\n    \t\t<a href=\"/user/368176\" class=\"l\">Shoegazer</a>\n<small class=\"grey\"> 玩过 </small>\n<small class=\"grey\">@ 2025-11-6 22:19</small>\n    \t\t<p class=\"comment\">云。喜剧和“科幻”部分非常好笑很下饭，一认真起来就尬了不少。唯一比较喜欢的角色是肖鹿，不过郑梓妍在林乐清初登场时的戏配上有趣的声线演得还挺甜的。</p><div class=\"likes_grid\" id=\"likes_grid_45053538\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"item clearit\" data-item-user=\"760548\">\n<a href=\"/user/760548\" class=\"avatar\"><span class=\"avatarNeue avatarSize32 ll\" style=\"background-image:url('//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/l/000/76/05/760548_9YDB1.jpg?r=1761249354&hd=1')\"></span></a>\n<div class=\"text_container text_main_even\">\n<div class=\"text\">\n<div class=\"actions_container\">\n<div class=\"post_actions\"></div>\n</div>\n\n    \t\t<a href=\"/user/760548\" class=\"l\">1O39</a>\n<span class=\"starstop-s\"><span class=\"starlight stars1\"></span></span><small class=\"grey\"> 抛弃 </small>\n<small class=\"grey\">@ 2025-10-27 16:49</small>\n    \t\t<p class=\"comment\">笑死我了，可以说是日本galgame瓦房店化的东西，更搞笑的是火了以后国内低能厂家跟风出了一大批这种劣质游戏，没办法喜欢看网文爽文的下沉市场就是这样的，只能说谁喜欢玩谁sb</p><div class=\"likes_grid\" id=\"likes_grid_44812576\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"item clearit\" data-item-user=\"837109\">\n<a href=\"/user/837109\" class=\"avatar\"><span class=\"avatarNeue avatarSize32 ll\" style=\"background-image:url('//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/l/000/83/71/837109.jpg?r=1730116385&hd=1')\"></span></a>\n<div class=\"text_container text_main_even\">\n<div class=\"text\">\n<div class=\"actions_container\">\n<div class=\"post_actions\"></div>\n</div>\n\n    \t\t<a href=\"/user/837109\" class=\"l\">Kanzaki Akito</a>\n<span class=\"starstop-s\"><span class=\"starlight stars5\"></span></span><small class=\"grey\"> 玩过 </small>\n<small class=\"grey\">@ 2025-10-23 01:44</small>\n    \t\t<p class=\"comment\">这分是给浩浩妈的</p><div class=\"likes_grid\" id=\"likes_grid_44694943\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"item clearit\" data-item-user=\"939812\">\n<a href=\"/user/939812\" class=\"avatar\"><span class=\"avatarNeue avatarSize32 ll\" style=\"background-image:url('//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/l/000/93/98/939812.jpg?r=1751045977&hd=1')\"></span></a>\n<div class=\"text_container text_main_even\">\n<div class=\"text\">\n<div class=\"actions_container\">\n<div class=\"post_actions\"></div>\n</div>\n\n    \t\t<a href=\"/user/939812\" class=\"l\">赤羽十烨</a>\n<span class=\"starstop-s\"><span class=\"starlight stars3\"></span></span><small class=\"grey\"> 玩过 </small>\n<small class=\"grey\">@ 2025-8-12 15:17</small>\n    \t\t<p class=\"comment\">气笑了这个游戏到底哪个神人写出来的剧本，你说演技多差也不至于，但就是令人感觉鸡皮疙瘩都起来的尴尬，唯一感觉不是很尴尬的是和兄弟在一起的时候</p><div class=\"likes_grid\" id=\"likes_grid_42476993\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"item clearit\" data-item-user=\"1079340\">\n<a href=\"/user/1079340\" class=\"avatar\"><span class=\"avatarNeue avatarSize32 ll\" style=\"background-image:url('//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/l/001/07/93/1079340_onwXo.jpg?r=1756974820&hd=1')\"></span></a>\n<div class=\"text_container text_main_even\">\n<div class=\"text\">\n<div class=\"actions_container\">\n<div class=\"post_actions\"></div>\n</div>\n\n    \t\t<a href=\"/user/1079340\" class=\"l\">花生米</a>\n<span class=\"starstop-s\"><span class=\"starlight stars6\"></span></span><small class=\"grey\"> 玩过 </small>\n<small class=\"grey\">@ 2025-8-2 13:05</small>\n    \t\t<p class=\"comment\">国产喜剧</p><div class=\"likes_grid\" id=\"likes_grid_42164728\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"item clearit\" data-item-user=\"1048339\">\n<a href=\"/user/1048339\" class=\"avatar\"><span class=\"avatarNeue avatarSize32 ll\" style=\"background-image:url('//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/l/icon.jpg')\"></span></a>\n<div class=\"text_container text_main_even\">\n<div class=\"text\">\n<div class=\"actions_container\">\n<div class=\"post_actions\"></div>\n</div>\n\n    \t\t<a href=\"/user/1048339\" class=\"l\">糖果树瀑布</a>\n<span class=\"starstop-s\"><span class=\"starlight stars3\"></span></span><small class=\"grey\"> 玩过 </small>\n<small class=\"grey\">@ 2025-6-26 23:23</small>\n    \t\t<p class=\"comment\">虽然还是烂 但比国g好 真的</p><div class=\"likes_grid\" id=\"likes_grid_40921526\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"item clearit\" data-item-user=\"718781\">\n<a href=\"/user/718781\" class=\"avatar\"><span class=\"avatarNeue avatarSize32 ll\" style=\"background-image:url('//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/l/000/71/87/718781.jpg?r=1708504491&hd=1')\"></span></a>\n<div class=\"text_container text_main_even\">\n<div class=\"text\">\n<div class=\"actions_container\">\n<div class=\"post_actions\"></div>\n</div>\n\n    \t\t<a href=\"/user/718781\" class=\"l\">不擅长捉弄的日奈酱</a>\n<span class=\"starstop-s\"><span class=\"starlight stars2\"></span></span><small class=\"grey\"> 玩过 </small>\n<small class=\"grey\">@ 2025-6-19 00:37</small>\n    \t\t<p class=\"comment\">剧情稀碎，人设稀烂</p><div class=\"likes_grid\" id=\"likes_grid_40687324\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"item clearit\" data-item-user=\"sakura0721\">\n<a href=\"/user/sakura0721\" class=\"avatar\"><span class=\"avatarNeue avatarSize32 ll\" style=\"background-image:url('//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/l/000/92/36/923676.jpg?r=1751294899&hd=1')\"></span></a>\n<div class=\"text_container text_main_even\">\n<div class=\"text\">\n<div class=\"actions_container\">\n<div class=\"post_actions\"></div>\n</div>\n\n    \t\t<a href=\"/user/sakura0721\" class=\"l\">我是翔子厨</a>\n<span class=\"starstop-s\"><span class=\"starlight stars3\"></span></span><small class=\"grey\"> 玩过 </small>\n<small class=\"grey\">@ 2025-6-2 14:15</small>\n    \t\t<p class=\"comment\">之所以接触它，还是因为我蒸汽的家庭共享里突然多出来的，而且当时网上还有一堆实况流程，云完之后本来还没太大反应，结果看到好友吹这个，还给我看蒸汽的特别好评还有杰出剧情奖的提名，属实给我肺都气炸，当场给他踢出了家庭组。你要说这玩意是gal，我是很不认同的，硬要类比也是《暴雨》或者《底特律》那种互动电影，但剧情上远远比不上这两位，纯整活向的，就和当今的那种无脑爽文短剧类似。这种题材其实我几年前就见过国外出一堆类似的，比如《超级情圣》《不想死就按x》算是一些篇幅比较短的这种类型，而且实际上国外这种真人互动剧不算少，像是《late shift》《她目睹了血案》，只是大多并不以恋爱为主，反而是推理类型偏多。没想到在国外压根没多少市场的，在国内反而爆红，不由得感叹品味差异有些大。而现在竟然还出了一堆模仿的，可以看出投机者简直太多了，从我心底还是希望这些玩意褒姒</p><div class=\"likes_grid\" id=\"likes_grid_40226280\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"item clearit\" data-item-user=\"1030889\">\n<a href=\"/user/1030889\" class=\"avatar\"><span class=\"avatarNeue avatarSize32 ll\" style=\"background-image:url('//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/l/001/03/08/1030889.jpg?r=1748339939&hd=1')\"></span></a>\n<div class=\"text_container text_main_even\">\n<div class=\"text\">\n<div class=\"actions_container\">\n<div class=\"post_actions\"></div>\n</div>\n\n    \t\t<a href=\"/user/1030889\" class=\"l\">zzz蜘蛛</a>\n<span class=\"starstop-s\"><span class=\"starlight stars1\"></span></span><small class=\"grey\"> 抛弃 </small>\n<small class=\"grey\">@ 2025-5-27 16:35</small>\n    \t\t<p class=\"comment\">喜欢玩的都是没见过幕刃的狗屎宅男</p><div class=\"likes_grid\" id=\"likes_grid_40042880\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div></div>\n<template id=\"likes_reaction_grid_item\" type=\"text/template\">\n    <a class=\"item {selected_class}\"\n          href=\"javascript:void(0);\"\n          data-like-type=\"{type}\"\n          data-like-main-id=\"{main_id}\"\n          data-like-related-id=\"{related_id}\"\n          data-like-value=\"{value}\"\n          title=\"{users}\"\n          data-toggle=\"tooltip\">\n        <span class=\"emoji\" style=\"background-image: url('/img/smiles/tv/{emoji}.gif');\"></span>\n        <span class=\"num\">{num}</span>\n    </a>\n</template>\n\n\n<script>\n        var data_likes_list = {\"40226280\":{\"54\":{\"type\":40,\"main_id\":\"460529\",\"value\":\"54\",\"total\":12,\"emoji\":\"15\",\"users\":[{\"username\":\"violinfeeling\",\"nickname\"